{"article_id":"JoCGgKQ7t9hY9tac","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON-House Republican leadership indicated on Wednesday","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"they had White House support on their plan","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to put two immigration bills forward ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"but it was unclear if that would be enough","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"for a bill to pass in Congress .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"In a deal","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"struck with centrists and conservative members of the conference ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he would hold votes next week on legislation","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that will protect young immigrants","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"brought to the U.S. as minors and living in the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"without authorization ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"as well as increase funding for border security .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The deal staved off an uprising from centrist Republicans","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"who were aiming to force votes on a series of immigration measures .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Party leaders had ratcheted up negotiations","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to avert a vote on bills","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"supported mostly by Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"they fear will infuriate their base of loyal GOP voters .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"\" This represents a consensus between our members","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"so that we can move forward on the immigration issue , \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Ryan said Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" Now what we have is an actual chance","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"at making law","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and solving this problem . \"","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Under the new agreement , Republican leaders would set up votes on both a conservative measure","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"offered previously by Reps. Bob Goodlatte","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"( R. , Va. )","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"and Michael McCaul","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"( R. , Texas ) ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and a compromise bill","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that was the subject of weeks of negotiations .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"The options","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"being considered as part of a compromise","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"include the creation of a new merit-based green card program","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that would reward immigrants for meeting certain benchmarks","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to allow them to eventually become citizens .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"President Donald Trump ended the Obama-era Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals , or DACA , program","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and has repeatedly called on Congress to replace it with legislation .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" It will be a merit-based system","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and we ' ll release what those merits are , \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"said Rep. Jeff Denham","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"( R. , Calif. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"who was part of the negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"\" But certainly those","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that came out of the shadows","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"and did what the government asked them to do ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"their time in the DACA program will count toward this as well . \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"But even members","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"who were part of the negotiations","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"were reluctant to commit their support for the deal on Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Florida Rep. Carlos Curbelo , one of the centrist Republicans","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"involved in negotiations ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"he was waiting to see the legislative text","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"to decide whether to support it .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"North Carolina Rep. Mark Meadows ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"who leads the conservative House Freedom Caucus ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"he was withholding support","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"because the details in the bill could change .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" The concrete has been poured in the forms ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"it is yet to set , \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"using a construction analogy .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" You can still make handprints in it ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"you can write your name in it ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"but it ' s far from set . \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"White House senior adviser Stephen Miller ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"speaking at a lunch meeting of House Republicans on Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"indicated","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Mr. Trump would support for the legislation ,","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"but didn ' t get into details .","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"Should a bill pass the House ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"it could face difficulties in the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"A bill","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"reflecting the president ' s priorities","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"failed in the Senate in February in a 39-60 vote ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"with 14 Republicans opposed .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"( R. , Ky. )","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"has said","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"he has no desire to spend time on bills","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"that are bound to fail .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Mr. Trump has said","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"legal protections for hundreds of thousands of so-called Dreamers , young people","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"brought to the U.S. illegally by their parents ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"must be paired with tighter border security ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"including funding for a wall along the Mexican border .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"He also wants curbs to the family-based migration system and an end to the diversity visa lottery ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"which admits 50,000 people","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"chosen at random from underrepresented countries .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"The border security provisions in the compromise bill are the same as those in the bill from Mssrs . McCaul and Goodlatte ,","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"according to Mr. Curbelo","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"( R. , Fla. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"who was also part of the negotiations .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"The compromise legislation eliminates the diversity visa lottery system","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"and changes family-based immigration ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"though Mr. Denham said","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"those specifics were not ironed out .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Excluded from the bill are provisions","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"overhauling the guest-worker program and a federal e-verify program .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Leadership said","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"those will be addressed in July ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"according to lawmakers in the meeting .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"Democrats indicated opposition to the plan on Wednesday .","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"Though House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi said","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"she hadn ' t been briefed on the legislation ,","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"she said","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"she would likely ask Democrats to vote against the Republican compromise bill","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"based on \" what we ' ve heard of it . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":180,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":116,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":0,"right